*libsfml-1.6 (06 Aug 2010)

  06 Aug 2010; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> +libsfml-1.6.ebuild,
  +files/libsfml-1.6-deps-and-cflags.patch,
  +files/libsfml-1.6-destdir.patch:
  Bumped courtesy of Tim Harder from b.g.o. The old version seems to be
  causing some problems with newer versions of sys-devel/patch.

